*pandas is open sourse library built on top of numpy
*it allows for fast analysis and data cleaning and preperation
*it excels in performance and productivity
*it also has built in visualization feature
*it can work with data from variety of sources

#-----------------------------------------------------
* to install it using conda just type -- conda install pandas
* to install it using pip3 just fire --- pip3 install pandas
